{"tid":228718,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民建制迷你飯局 搞手廖長江稱純粹「傾吓計」","createTime":"2017-05-04T06:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T06:17:05.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d27f22bb4fcab4d1ff79dc5bc3c6d1ef7e9ced80","tid":228718,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170504/large/1493875165_78af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170504%2Flarge%2F1493875165_78af.jpg&h=f57eeb60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主派和建制派舉行飯局，有共10名議員現身，包括民主黨胡志偉、公民黨楊岳橋、郭榮鏗、民建聯李慧琼、陳克勤、工聯會黃國健、自由黨鍾國斌、新民黨葉劉淑儀、經民聯林健鋒及無政黨廖長江。<br />\n<br />\n林健鋒到場時稱，建制派各大板塊經常聚首，約2、3個月前李慧琼提出聯絡反對派代表一同用膳「傾計」，然後由建制派「班長」廖長江作東及穿針引線。他續指今次飯局並無特定議題如外界所指的八黨聯盟，純粹「傾吓計」，被問到是否「吹和風」的開始，林認為外界毋須太多揣測。<br />\n<br />\n另外，議員陸續到場期間，教局局長吳克儉巧合地突然現身，不過他未有回應傳媒提問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56649188&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56649188%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170504&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3qMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=0b02d579\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56649188%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170504&h=8eab670a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56649188&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170504</a>"},{"pid":"922150a0c1ca0dad6bb641eefb36f49557dd07b8","tid":228718,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:07:34.000Z","msg":"我淨係見到成枱建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民主派呢？作新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"984d47bc3de